text: Logo of Nord Pool ASA Nord Pool ASA was a company in existence between 1996 and 2010. Reference is made to the two articles about its present successors: * Nord Pool, previously Nord Pool Spot AS, a subsidy of Nord Pool ASA until it was spun off in 2001 * NASDAQ OMX Commodities Europe, also known as "Nord Pool" as a result of Nasdaq OMX's acquisition of some of Nord Pool ASA's assets.
title: Nord Pool ASA
